Selecting all pets and their owners, if they have one
SELECT posts.ID,posts.title,users.firstname,users.lastname,users.email FROM posts LEFT JOIN users ON users.ID=posts.owner_ID

All users and their pets, if they have one
SELECT users.firstname, users.lastname, users.email, posts.title FROM users LEFT JOIN posts ON users.ID=posts.owner_ID

All pets owned by a specific users (Id = 14)
SELECT users.firstname, users.lastname, users.email, posts.title FROM users LEFT JOIN posts ON users.ID=posts.owner_ID WHERE users.ID=14 

Display all the pets published by a specific user (Id = 14)
SELECT users.firstname, users.lastname, users.email, posts.title FROM users LEFT JOIN posts ON users.ID=posts.user_ID WHERE users.ID=14 

All pets and all shelters
SELECT posts.ID,posts.title,users.firstname,users.lastname,users.email FROM posts LEFT JOIN users ON users.ID=posts.user_ID